-- MOVES-ACE names Edward Ler as president director for Indonesia's general insurance business
-- 
-- Mon Oct 27, 2014 05:11AM EDT
-- None



Oct 27 (Reuters) - U.S. insurer ACE Ltd <ACE.N> appointed Edward Ler as president director for Indonesia's general insurance business.

Ler will report to Juan Luis Ortega, regional president in Asia-Pacific. [ID:nBw2WznHLa] Presently, Ler is the regional head of ACE's personal lines and business insurance.